'''Christopher Routis''' (born 3 March 1990) is a [[France|French]] [[association football|footballer]] who plays for [[Servette FC|Servette]] in the [[Swiss Super League]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Christopher Routis|url=http://www.transfermarkt.co.uk/en/christopher-routis/leistungsdaten-detail/spieler_153776.html|publisher=transfermarkt.co.uk}}</ref>

